'''克里斯托弗·查尔斯·米勒'''（{{lang-en|Christopher Charles Miller}}，{{bd|1965年|10月15日}}<ref name="QuestionaireSenCom">{{cite web |title=Questionnaire for Completion by Presidential Nominees |url=https://www.intelligence.senate.gov/sites/default/files/documents/q-cmiller-072220.pdf |website=U.S. Senate Select Committee on Intelligence |publisher=United States Senate |accessdate=2020-11-09 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109201601/https://www.intelligence.senate.gov/sites/default/files/documents/q-cmiller-072220.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>），[[美国国防部|美国国防部]]官员，曾任{{tsl|en|National Counterterrorism Center|国家反恐中心}}主任<ref name="PN1741 - nomination of Christopher C Miller"/><ref name="NCTC Bio">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2020-08-10|title=Christopher Miller, Director of NCTC|url=https://www.dni.gov/files/NCTC/documents/leadership_biographies/DNCTC_Miller_Biography.pdf|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109185212/https://www.dni.gov/files/NCTC/documents/leadership_biographies/DNCTC_Miller_Biography.pdf|archive-date=2020-11-09|access-date=|website=}}</ref><ref name="Beavers Trump fires Defense chief"/>。2020年11月9日获总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]委任为代理[[美国国防部长|美国国防部长]]，接替被开除的[[馬克·埃斯柏|馬克·埃斯柏]]<ref name="nyt-firing" >{{cite news |last1=Cooper |first1=Helene |last2=Schmitt |first2=Eric |title=Trump Fires Mark Esper, His Defense Secretary |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/09/us/politics/esper-defense-secretary.html |accessdate=2020-11-09 |publisher=New York Times |date=2020-11-09 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109181103/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/09/us/politics/esper-defense-secretary.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dni.gov/index.php/nctc-who-we-are/director-nctc|title=Director NCTC|website=www.dni.gov|accessdate=2020-11-10|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109190023/https://www.dni.gov/index.php/nctc-who-we-are/director-nctc|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Christopher C. Miller - defense.gov">{{Cite web|url=https://www.defense.gov/Our-Story/Biographies/Biography/Article/2111192/christopher-c-miller/|title=Christopher C. Miller|website=www.defense.gov|accessdate=2020-11-10|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109183146/https://www.defense.gov/Our-Story/Biographies/Biography/Article/2111192/christopher-c-miller/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet|title=I am pleased to announce that Christopher C. Miller, the highly respected Director of the National Counterterrorism Center (unanimously confirmed by the Senate), will be Acting Secretary of Defense, effective immediately.. |user=realDonaldTrump|number=1325859406349799424 |accessdate=2020-11-09|date=2020-11-09}}</ref>。

== 早年及教育 ==
米勒生于美国[[威斯康星州|威斯康星州]]{{tsl|en|Platteville, Wisconsin|普拉特维尔 (威斯康星州)|普拉特维尔}}，母亲是路易丝·马辛（Lois Maxine），父亲是哈维·D·米勒（Harvey D. Miller），其后在[[艾奥瓦州|艾奥瓦州]][[艾奥瓦城_(艾奥瓦州)|艾奥瓦城]]长大<ref>{{cite news |title=Neighbors |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/62881090/iowa-city-press-citizen/ |accessdate=2020-11-09 |work=Iowa City Press-Citizen |date=1984-08-29 |pages=32 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112094812/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/62881090/iowa-city-press-citizen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Neighbors |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/62881598/iowa-city-press-citizen/ |accessdate=2020-11-09 |work=Iowa City Press-Citizen |date=2001-03-02 |pages=23 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112102457/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/62881598/iowa-city-press-citizen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。高中就读于{{tsl|en|Iowa City High School|艾奥瓦城高中}}，其后获[[乔治·华盛顿大学|乔治·华盛顿大学]]历史文学士学位，凭借年级最高[[成绩|绩点]]获[[加德纳·格林·赫巴德|加德纳·格林·赫巴德]]美国历史纪念奖<ref>{{cite news |title=Neighbors |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/62902018/neighbors/ |accessdate=2020-11-09 |work=Iowa City Press-Citizen |date=1987-06-03 |pages=36 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112094835/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/62902018/neighbors/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2001年获[[美国国防大学|美国国防大学]][[海军战争学院|海军战争学院]]国家安全文学士学位<ref>{{Cite web|title=President Donald J. Trump Announces Intent to Nominate Individual to a Key Administration Post|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/president-donald-j-trump-announces-intent-nominate-individual-key-administration-post-22/|access-date=2020-11-09|website=The White House|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109191552/https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/president-donald-j-trump-announces-intent-nominate-individual-key-administration-post-22/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="QuestionaireSenCom"/>。他也毕业于海军指挥参谋学院及{{tsl|en|United States Army War College|美国陆军战争学院|陆军战争学院}}<ref name="Christopher C. Miller - defense.gov"/>。

== 生涯 ==
米勒曾是前[[美國陸軍特種部隊|陆军特种部队]]队员<ref name="nyt-firing" />，1983年至2014年服役<ref name="NCTC Bio"/>，參加了在阿富汗和伊拉克戰爭。在阿富汗，他是{{Link-en|美國陸軍第5特戰群|5th Special Forces Group (United States)|第5特戰群}}的連長，該特戰群與基地組織和塔利班作戰。在伊拉克，他於2006年和2007年指揮特種部隊。於2009年12月晉升為上校。作為陸軍軍官的最後一項任務是在國防部五角大樓特種作戰、低強度衝突與相互依存能力助理部長室擔任特種作戰和不規則戰爭主任。其后担任[[国防工业|国防承包商]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Defense Sec. Mark Esper Ousted by Trump |url=https://spectrumlocalnews.com/nys/buffalo/news/2020/11/09/trump-fires-mark-esper-as-defense-secretary- |accessdate=2020-11-09 |work=spectrumlocalnews.com |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109185045/https://spectrumlocalnews.com/nys/buffalo/news/2020/11/09/trump-fires-mark-esper-as-defense-secretary- |dead-url=no }}</ref>。担任[[美国国家安全委员会|美国国家安全委员会]]反恐顾问期间<ref>{{Cite news|last=Cooper|first=Helene|last2=Schmitt|first2=Eric|date=2020-11-09|title=Trump Fires Mark Esper, His Defense Secretary|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/09/us/politics/esper-defense-secretary.html|access-date=2020-11-09|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109181103/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/09/us/politics/esper-defense-secretary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Beavers Trump fires Defense chief"/>，负责打击[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]的军事行动<ref name="Trump Ousts Defense Chief Esper">{{cite news |title=Trump Ousts Defense Chief Esper Who Balked at Loyalty Demand |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-09/trump-ousts-esper-as-defense-secretary-after-a-rocky-tenure |accessdate=2020-11-09 |work=Bloomberg.com |date=2020-11-09 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109182122/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-09/trump-ousts-esper-as-defense-secretary-after-a-rocky-tenure |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随后出任国防部副助理秘书，负责特种作战及反恐行动<ref name="Beavers Trump fires Defense chief"/><ref name="Christopher C. Miller - defense.gov"/>，任内将[[伊朗|伊朗]]、[[真主党|真主党]]和{{tsl|en|Domestic terrorism in the United States|美国本土恐怖主义|本土恐怖组织}}认定为国家威胁<ref name="Trump Ousts Defense Chief Esper"/><ref name="Trump plans to nominate Special Forces veteran to head counterterrorism center amid uncertainty about its future"/>。

2020年3月，获总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]提名为{{tsl|en|National Counterterrorism Center|国家反恐中心}}主任<ref name="Trump plans to nominate Special Forces veteran to head counterterrorism center amid uncertainty about its future">{{cite news |title=Trump plans to nominate Special Forces veteran to head counterterrorism center amid uncertainty about its future |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/christopher-miller-national-counterterrorism-center/2020/03/18/1590b98e-691c-11ea-b313-df458622c2cc_story.html |accessdate=2020-11-09 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109175838/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/christopher-miller-national-counterterrorism-center/2020/03/18/1590b98e-691c-11ea-b313-df458622c2cc_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，8月6日获参议院通过<ref name="Beavers Trump fires Defense chief">{{cite news |last1=Beavers |first1=Olivia |title=Trump fires Defense chief Mark Esper |url=https://thehill.com/policy/defense/524728-trump-fires-defense-chief-esper |accessdate=2020-11-09 |work=TheHill |date=2020-11-09 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109180104/https://thehill.com/policy/defense/524728-trump-fires-defense-chief-esper |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Trump Ousts Defense Chief Esper"/><ref name="PN1741 - nomination of Christopher C Miller">{{cite web |title=PN1741 - Nomination of Christopher C. Miller for Office of the Director of National Intelligence, 116th Congress (2019-2020) |url=https://www.congress.gov/nomination/116th-congress/1741 |website=www.congress.gov |accessdate=2020-11-09 |date=2020-08-06 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109180929/https://www.congress.gov/nomination/116th-congress/1741 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，8月10日履新<ref name="Trump Ousts Defense Chief Esper"/>。

2020年11月9日，特朗普委任米勒出任代[[美国国防部长|国防部长]]，接替[[馬克·埃斯柏|馬克·埃斯柏]]<ref name="Beavers Trump fires Defense chief"/>。此举违反了国防部长职位悬空时应由副部长接替的联邦法律规定<ref>{{cite news |last1=Spinelli |first1=Dan |title=Trump “Terminated” Defense Secretary Mark Esper |url=https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2020/11/trump-terminated-defense-secretary-mark-esper/ |accessdate=2020-11-11 |work=Mother Jones |date=2020-11-09 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124194436/https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2020/11/trump-terminated-defense-secretary-mark-esper/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Ackerman |first1=Spencer |title=Mark Esper, Who Flinched at Military Crackdown, Out at Pentagon |url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/mark-esper-who-flinched-at-military-crackdown-out-at-pentagon |accessdate=2020-11-11 |work=The Daily Beast |date=2020-11-09 |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211233144/https://www.thedailybeast.com/mark-esper-who-flinched-at-military-crackdown-out-at-pentagon |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同样，根据美国宪法确保[[軍隊國家化|文人領軍]]的规定，国防部长在接受任命前的七年内不得在军中服役，除非国会特准<ref>{{cite web |title=Here's why officers can't easily become defense secretaries |url=https://www.militarytimes.com/news/pentagon-congress/2016/12/02/here-s-why-officers-can-t-easily-become-defense-secretaries/ |website=Militray Times |accessdate=2020-11-13 |date=2016-12-02 |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211142353/https://www.militarytimes.com/news/pentagon-congress/2016/12/02/here-s-why-officers-can-t-easily-become-defense-secretaries/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==个人生活==
米勒与妻子凯西·马格·米勒（Kathryn Maag Miller）于1989年9月16日结婚<ref name="MarriageAnnouncement">{{cite news |title=Marriage of Maag |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/62898472/marriage-of-maag-miller/ |accessdate=2020-11-09 |work=Iowa City Press-Citizen |date=1989-09-19 |pages=15 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112160921/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/62898472/marriage-of-maag-miller/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，凯西是某健康及环境游说集团的办公室经理<ref name="QuestionaireSenCom"/>，两人育有三个孩子<ref name="NCTC Bio"/>。

